  "fullSource": "use IO.Std.write_line;\n\nfibs() -> Collections.Iterable[int] is\n    let a mut = 0;\n    let b mut = 1;\n    do\n        yield a;\n        let next = a + b;\n        a = b;\n        b = next;\n    od\nsi\n\nentry() is\n    let count mut = 0;\n    for f in fibs() do\n        write_line(f);\n        count = count + 1;\n        if count >= 8 then\n            break;\n        fi\n    od\nsi\n",
